@baseUrl = http://localhost:5180

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BATTERY
# Charge rate (drone.yaml): 0.10 % / s  →  full charge ≈ 16 min 40 s
# Emergency land threshold: 10 %
# Recharge requires: Idle state
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Battery Status
# Returns: batteryPercent, isCharging, droneState, timestamp
GET {{baseUrl}}/drone/battery
Accept: application/json

###

### Start Recharge
# Requires: Idle state
# Transitions drone: Idle → Charging
# Charging stops automatically when battery reaches 100 %.
POST {{baseUrl}}/drone/battery/recharge

###

### Stop Recharge
# Requires: Charging state
# Transitions drone: Charging → Idle
POST {{baseUrl}}/drone/battery/recharge/stop

###
